          The CLR code generation team blog     ponders          To NGen or Not to NGen? 
          Behind the Code          interviews Patrick Dussud     on the subject of garbage collection. 
     Kim Hamilton from     the     BCL Team     discusses the complex issue of long paths in a three-part series:          Part 1,          Part 2,          Part 3,          Part 3. 


        
                

        
		
                

            
            
                
